data.description: AFFORDABLE 3 BR home in great neighborhood!    This 3 BR, 2 bath jewel is SOOOOO easy to access to I-65 and all points north or south!    Beautiful 1-level home w/fenced yard - AND - a screened patio to enjoy this magnificent weather!    This seller has loved and maintained this home and it shows!   New roof, new AC, new toilets in 2023.    New flooring in 2022.   All appliances remain and new Washer & Dryer are negotiable as well.  Floored attic for plenty of storage space.   Comes with a security system that buyer can simply transfer!  Club House and Pool can be rented for private parties; there's even a basketball goal to enjoy a game!  So easy to plan birthday parties, etc. - esp. in summer months!
